OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIceland boss retracts HIV  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fneedle staff attack claim  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of Iceland has been forced to 
OL,6, apologise and retract a claim that     
OL,7, three staff contracted HIV as a result 
OL,8, of needle attacks.                     
OL,10,FRichard Walker said he made comments in
OL,11,F"error" in a "draft article" about     
OL,12,Fthreats of violence against store      
OL,13,Fworkers by shoplifters for Mail Online.
OL,15,FPoliticians and charities had called   
OL,16,Ffor him to withdraw the claims, stating
OL,17,Fthat such comments set back "work to   
OL,18,Fdispel myths around HIV".              
OL,20,FMr Walker said he had "learnt a lot".  
